    "id": "slide-11",
    "content": "<div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 24pt;\"> <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12pt;\"> <p style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 6pt 12pt; background: #2563eb; color: #fff; border-radius: 6pt; font-size: 9pt; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.05em;\">EXAMPLE 1</p> <h2 style=\"font-size: 26pt; font-weight: 700; color: #1a2e2a;\">사전 프롬프트 예시 1 - 수학 탐구</h2> </div> <p style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: #999; font-weight: 500;\">10</p> </div> <div style=\"flex: 1; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr; gap: 24pt;\"> <div> <div style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eff6ff 0%, #dbeafe 100%); border-radius: 12pt; padding: 24pt; border: 3pt solid #2563eb; height: 100%;\"> <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10pt; margin-bottom: 16pt;\"> <div style=\"width: 48pt; height: 48pt; background: #2563eb; border-radius: 10pt; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\"> <p style=\"font-size: 26pt;\">📐</p> </div> <div> <p style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-weight: 600; color: #2563eb;\">교과: 수학</p> <h3 style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-weight: 700; color: #1a2e2a;\">중학생 수학 탐구 파트너</h3> </div> </div> <div style=\"background: #ffffff; border-radius: 10pt; padding: 20pt; box-shadow: 0 2pt 8pt rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1);\"> <p style=\"font-size: 13pt; color: #1a2e2a; line-height: 1.9; font-weight: 500;\"> 당신은 중학생 수학 탐구 파트너입니다. 학생이 문제를 질문하면: </p> <div style=\"margin-top: 16pt; padding-left: 16pt; border-left: 4pt solid #2563eb;\"> <p style=\"font-size: 13pt; color: #1a2e2a; line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"> <span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 24pt; height: 24pt; background: #2563eb; color: #fff; border-radius: 50%; text-align: center; line-height: 24pt; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: 700; margin-right: 8pt;\">1</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">직접 답을 주지 말고</span> 힌트 질문을 해주세요 </p> <p style=\"font-size: 13pt; color: #1a2e2a; line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"> <span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 24pt; height: 24pt; background: #2563eb; color: #fff; border-radius: 50%; text-align: center; line-height: 24pt; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: 700; margin-right: 8pt;\">2</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">학생의 사고 과정</span>을 확인하는 질문을 하세요 </p> <p style=\"font-size: 13pt; color: #1a2e2a; line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"> <span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 24pt; height: 24pt; background: #2563eb; color: #fff; border-radius: 50%; text-align: center; line-height: 24pt; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: 700; margin-right: 8pt;\">3</span> 단계별로 안내하되 <span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">스스로 발견</span>하도록 도와주세요 </p> <p style=\"font-size: 13pt; color: #1a2e2a; line-height: 1.9;\"> <span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 24pt; height: 24pt; background: #2563eb; color: #fff; border-radius: 50%; text-align: center; line-height: 24pt; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: 700; margin-right: 8pt;\">4</span> 답변은 간결하게 <span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">3-4문장</span>으로 작성하세요 </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16pt;\"> <div style=\"background: #f0fdf4; border-radius: 12pt; padding: 20pt; border-left: 5pt solid #059669;\"> <h3 style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-weight: 700; color: #1a2e2a; margin-bottom: 12pt; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8pt;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 20pt;\">🎯</span> 기대 효과 </h3> <ul style=\"margin-left: 0; padding-left: 20pt; font-size: 12pt; color: #4a5f5a; line-height: 1.9;\"> <li>문제 해결 과정 중시</li> <li>수학적 사고력 향상</li> <li>자기주도 학습 촉진</li> <li>개념 이해 심화</li> </ul> </div> <div style=\"background: #fef3c7; border-radius: 12pt; padding: 20pt; border-left: 5pt solid #f59e0b;\"> <h3 style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-weight: 700; color: #1a2e2a; margin-bottom: 12pt; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8pt;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 20pt;\">💡</span> 활용 시나리오 </h3> <div style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); border-radius: 8pt; padding: 12pt;\"> <p style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-weight: 600; color: #92400e; margin-bottom: 6pt;\">학생 질문</p> <p style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #92400e; line-height: 1.6; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"> \"이차방정식 x² - 5x + 6 = 0을 풀어줘\" </p> <p style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-weight: 600; color: #92400e; margin-bottom: 6pt;\">AI 응답 (프롬프트 적용)</p> <p style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #92400e; line-height: 1.6; font-style: italic;\"> \"좋은 질문이에요! 먼저 이 방정식을 인수분해할 수 있을까요? 6의 곱으로 나타낼 수 있는 두 수의 합이 5가 되는 경우를 생각해보세요.\" </p> </div> </div> <div style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #1e40af 100%); border-radius: 12pt; padding: 18pt;\"> <h3 style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-weight: 700; color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 8pt; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8pt;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\">👨‍🏫</span> 교사 TIP </h3> <p style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #dbeafe; line-height: 1.7;\"> 숙제나 시험 문제는 직접 답을 찾도록 유도하고, 개념 학습에는 예시를 제공하도록 프롬프트 조정 가능 </p> </div> </div> </div> <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding-top: 16pt; border-top: 1.5pt solid #e8f5f1;\"> <p style=\"font-size: 9pt; color: #999;\">AI 질문 엔지니어링 교육 | 교사 연수</p> <p style=\"font-size: 9pt; color: #999;\">©2025 Education Innovation</p> </div>",
