    "content": "<div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 28pt;\"> <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12pt;\"> <p style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 6pt 12pt; background: #2563eb; color: #fff; border-radius: 6pt; font-size: 9pt; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.05em;\">PRACTICE 1</p> <h2 style=\"font-size: 28pt; font-weight: 700; color: #1a2e2a;\">실전 활동 예시 1 - 질문 개선하기</h2> </div> <p style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: #999; font-weight: 500;\">15</p> </div> <div style=\"flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 24pt;\"> <div style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fee2e2 0%, #fecaca 100%); border-radius: 16pt; padding: 28pt; border: 3pt solid #dc2626;\"> <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12pt; margin-bottom: 16pt;\"> <div style=\"width: 56pt; height: 56pt; background: #dc2626; border-radius: 12pt; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\"> <p style=\"font-size: 28pt;\">❌</p> </div> <div> <p style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-weight: 600; color: #dc2626;\">BEFORE</p> <h3 style=\"font-size: 20pt; font-weight: 700; color: #1a2e2a;\">개선 전 질문</h3> </div> </div> <div style=\"background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12pt; padding: 24pt;\"> <p style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #1a2e2a; line-height: 1.6; font-style: italic; font-weight: 500;\"> \"광합성이 뭐야?\" </p> </div> <div style=\"margin-top: 16pt; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); border-radius: 8pt; padding: 14pt;\"> <p style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-weight: 700; color: #991b1b; margin-bottom: 8pt;\">⚠️ 문제점 분석</p> <ul style=\"margin-left: 20pt; font-size: 12pt; color: #991b1b; line-height: 1.8;\"> <li>질문 목적이 불명확함</li> <li>학습 수준이 제시되지 않음</li> <li>답변 형식 지정 없음</li> <li>단편적인 답변만 받을 가능성 높음</li> </ul> </div> </div> <div style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d1fae5 0%, #a7f3d0 100%); border-radius: 16pt; padding: 28pt; border: 3pt solid #059669;\"> <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12pt; margin-bottom: 16pt;\"> <div style=\"width: 56pt; height: 56pt; background: #059669; border-radius: 12pt; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\"> <p style=\"font-size: 28pt;\">✅</p> </div> <div> <p style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-weight: 600; color: #059669;\">AFTER</p> <h3 style=\"font-size: 20pt; font-weight: 700; color: #1a2e2a;\">개선 후 질문</h3> </div> </div> <div style=\"background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12pt; padding: 24pt;\"> <p style=\"font-size: 17pt; color: #1a2e2a; line-height: 1.7; font-weight: 500;\"> \"광합성을 <span style=\"background: #dbeafe; padding: 2pt 6pt; border-radius: 4pt; font-weight: 700;\">초등학생이 이해할 수 있게</span> <span style=\"background: #fef3c7; padding: 2pt 6pt; border-radius: 4pt; font-weight: 700;\">3단계로 나누어</span> 설명해주고, <span style=\"background: #e9d5ff; padding: 2pt 6pt; border-radius: 4pt; font-weight: 700;\">각 단계마다 실생활 비유를 들어줘</span>. 그리고 <span style=\"background: #fed7aa; padding: 2pt 6pt; border-radius: 4pt; font-weight: 700;\">내가 이해했는지 확인할 수 있는 질문도 해줘</span>.\" </p> </div> <div style=\"margin-top: 16pt; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 10pt;\"> <div style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); border-radius: 8pt; padding: 12pt; text-align: center;\"> <p style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-weight: 600; color: #065f46; margin-bottom: 4pt;\">CLEAR</p> <p style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: #065f46; line-height: 1.5;\">3단계 설명</p> </div> <div style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); border-radius: 8pt; padding: 12pt; text-align: center;\"> <p style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-weight: 600; color: #065f46; margin-bottom: 4pt;\">CONTEXT</p> <p style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: #065f46; line-height: 1.5;\">초등학생 수준</p> </div> <div style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); border-radius: 8pt; padding: 12pt; text-align: center;\"> <p style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-weight: 600; color: #065f46; margin-bottom: 4pt;\">CONSTRAINT</p> <p style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: #065f46; line-height: 1.5;\">실생활 비유</p> </div> <div style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); border-radius: 8pt; padding: 12pt; text-align: center;\"> <p style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-weight: 600; color: #065f46; margin-bottom: 4pt;\">CHECK</p> <p style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: #065f46; line-height: 1.5;\">확인 질문</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div style=\"background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #059669 100%); border-radius: 12pt; padding: 18pt; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16pt; margin-top: 16pt;\"> <p style=\"font-size: 32pt;\">🎯</p> <div style=\"flex: 1;\"> <p style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-weight: 700; color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 6pt;\">수업 활동 제안</p> <p style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #e0f2fe; line-height: 1.6;\"> 학생들에게 \"나쁜 질문\"을 주고 짝과 함께 \"좋은 질문\"으로 개선하는 활동을 진행해보세요. 개선 과정을 발표하며 서로 배울 수 있습니다. </p> </div> </div> <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding-top: 16pt; border-top: 1.5pt solid #e8f5f1;\"> <p style=\"font-size: 9pt; color: #999;\">AI 질문 엔지니어링 교육 | 교사 연수</p> <p style=\"font-size: 9pt; color: #999;\">©2025 Education Innovation</p> </div>",
