    "id": "slide-17",
    "content": "<div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 24pt;\"> <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12pt;\"> <p style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 6pt 12pt; background: #059669; color: #fff; border-radius: 6pt; font-size: 9pt; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.05em;\">PRACTICE 2</p> <h2 style=\"font-size: 28pt; font-weight: 700; color: #1a2e2a;\">실전 활동 예시 2 - 탐구 심화</h2> </div> <p style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: #4a5f5a; font-weight: 500;\">16</p> </div> <div style=\"flex: 1; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 16pt; padding: 32pt; box-shadow: 0 4pt 16pt rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\"> <div style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 24pt;\"> <h3 style=\"font-size: 20pt; font-weight: 700; color: #1a2e2a; margin-bottom: 8pt;\">단계적 질문으로 탐구 심화하기</h3> <p style=\"font-size: 13pt; color: #4a5f5a;\">하나의 주제를 3단계 질문으로 깊이 있게 탐구하는 방법</p> </div> <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20pt;\"> <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 20pt;\"> <div style=\"min-width: 80pt; text-align: center;\"> <div style=\"width: 80pt; height: 80pt; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb 0%, #3b82f6 100%); border-radius: 16pt; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 8pt;\"> <p style=\"font-size: 28pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: 700;\">1</p> <p style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); font-weight: 600;\">STEP</p> </div> <p style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-weight: 600; color: #2563eb;\">기본 이해</p> </div> <div style=\"flex: 1; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eff6ff 0%, #dbeafe 100%); border-radius: 12pt; padding: 20pt; border-left: 5pt solid #2563eb;\"> <p style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-weight: 700; color: #1a2e2a; margin-bottom: 10pt;\">1차 질문: 개념 파악</p> <p style=\"font-size: 15pt; color: #1a2e2a; line-height: 1.7; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"> \"기후 변화의 원인이 뭐야?\" </p> <div style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); border-radius: 8pt; padding: 12pt;\"> <p style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-weight: 600; color: #1e40af; margin-bottom: 6pt;\">💭 예상 답변</p> <p style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #4a5f5a; line-height: 1.6;\"> 온실가스 증가, 화석연료 사용, 삼림 파괴 등 기본 개념 설명 </p> </div> </div> </div> <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 20pt;\"> <div style=\"min-width: 80pt; text-align: center;\"> <div style=\"width: 80pt; height: 80pt; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669 0%, #10b981 100%); border-radius: 16pt; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 8pt;\"> <p style=\"font-size: 28pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: 700;\">2</p> <p style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); font-weight: 600;\">STEP</p> </div> <p style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-weight: 600; color: #059669;\">분석 및 탐구</p> </div> <div style=\"flex: 1; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdf4 0%, #dcfce7 100%); border-radius: 12pt; padding: 20pt; border-left: 5pt solid #059669;\"> <p style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-weight: 700; color: #1a2e2a; margin-bottom: 10pt;\">2차 질문: 다각도 분석</p> <p style=\"font-size: 15pt; color: #1a2e2a; line-height: 1.7; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"> \"인간 활동이 기후 변화에 미치는 영향을 <span style=\"background: #fef3c7; padding: 2pt 6pt; border-radius: 4pt; font-weight: 700;\">3가지 측면</span>에서 분석해줘\" </p> <div style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); border-radius: 8pt; padding: 12pt;\"> <p style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-weight: 600; color: #065f46; margin-bottom: 6pt;\">💭 예상 답변</p> <p style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #4a5f5a; line-height: 1.6;\"> 환경적·경제적·사회적 측면에서 구조화된 분석, 각 측면의 구체적 사례와 데이터 </p> </div> </div> </div> <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 20pt;\"> <div style=\"min-width: 80pt; text-align: center;\"> <div style=\"width: 80pt; height: 80pt; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed 0%, #8b5cf6 100%); border-radius: 16pt; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 8pt;\"> <p style=\"font-size: 28pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: 700;\">3</p> <p style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); font-weight: 600;\">STEP</p> </div> <p style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-weight: 600; color: #7c3aed;\">해결책 모색</p> </div> <div style=\"flex: 1; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #faf5ff 0%, #f3e8ff 100%); border-radius: 12pt; padding: 20pt; border-left: 5pt solid #7c3aed;\"> <p style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-weight: 700; color: #1a2e2a; margin-bottom: 10pt;\">3차 질문: 비판적 사고</p> <p style=\"font-size: 15pt; color: #1a2e2a; line-height: 1.7; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"> \"각 원인에 대한 해결책을 <span style=\"background: #fef3c7; padding: 2pt 6pt; border-radius: 4pt; font-weight: 700;\">장단점과 함께</span> 제시해줘\" </p> <div style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); border-radius: 8pt; padding: 12pt;\"> <p style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-weight: 600; color: #5b21b6; margin-bottom: 6pt;\">💭 예상 답변</p> <p style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #4a5f5a; line-height: 1.6;\"> 다양한 해결책의 실현 가능성, 비용, 효과 등을 균형있게 분석한 심화 답변 </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div style=\"background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #7c3aed 100%); border-radius: 12pt; padding: 18pt; margin-top: 20pt; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16pt;\"> <p style=\"font-size: 32pt;\">🚀</p> <div style=\"flex: 1;\"> <p style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-weight: 700; color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 6pt;\">학습 효과</p> <p style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #e0f2fe; line-height: 1.6;\"> 단계적 질문으로 표면적 이해 → 깊이 있는 분석 → 비판적 사고까지 발전시킬 수 있습니다. 학생들이 스스로 질문의 깊이를 조절하는 법을 배웁니다. </p> </div> </div> <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding-top: 16pt; border-top: 1.5pt solid rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.2);\"> <p style=\"font-size: 9pt; color: #4a5f5a;\">AI 질문 엔지니어링 교육 | 교사 연수</p> <p style=\"font-size: 9pt; color: #4a5f5a;\">©2025 Education Innovation</p> </div>",
