    "content": "<div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 28pt;\"> <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12pt;\"> <p style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 6pt 12pt; background: #0891b2; color: #fff; border-radius: 6pt; font-size: 9pt; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.05em;\">APPLICATION</p> <h2 style=\"font-size: 28pt; font-weight: 700; color: #1a2e2a;\">수업 적용 시나리오</h2> </div> <p style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: #999; font-weight: 500;\">17</p> </div> <div style=\"flex: 1;\"> <div style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 24pt;\"> <h3 style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-weight: 700; color: #1a2e2a; margin-bottom: 8pt;\">AI 질문 엔지니어링 수업 5단계</h3> <p style=\"font-size: 13pt; color: #4a5f5a;\">한 차시 수업에 바로 적용할 수 있는 단계별 가이드</p> </div> <div style=\"position: relative;\"> <div style=\"position: absolute; left: 40pt; top: 36pt; bottom: 36pt; width: 3pt; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #2563eb 0%, #059669 20%, #0891b2 40%, #7c3aed 60%, #ea580c 100%);\"></div> <div style=\"display: flex; gap: 20pt; margin-bottom: 16pt; position: relative; z-index: 1;\"> <div style=\"min-width: 80pt; text-align: center;\"> <div style=\"width: 80pt; height: 72pt; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb 0%, #3b82f6 100%); border-radius: 12pt; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; box-shadow: 0 4pt 12pt rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.3);\"> <p style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4pt;\">STEP 1</p> <p style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: 700;\">준비</p> </div> </div> <div style=\"flex: 1; background: #eff6ff; border-radius: 10pt; padding: 16pt; border-left: 4pt solid #2563eb;\"> <h4 style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-weight: 700; color: #1a2e2a; margin-bottom: 8pt;\">교사가 사전 프롬프트 설정</h4> <p style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #4a5f5a; line-height: 1.7;\"> 수업 주제와 학생 수준에 맞는 AI 역할과 응답 원칙을 미리 설정합니다. 학습 목표에 따라 탐구형, 개념 이해형 등 프롬프트 유형을 선택하세요. </p> </div> </div> <div style=\"display: flex; gap: 20pt; margin-bottom: 16pt; position: relative; z-index: 1;\"> <div style=\"min-width: 80pt; text-align: center;\"> <div style=\"width: 80pt; height: 72pt; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669 0%, #10b981 100%); border-radius: 12pt; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; box-shadow: 0 4pt 12pt rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.3);\"> <p style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4pt;\">STEP 2</p> <p style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: 700;\">안내</p> </div> </div> <div style=\"flex: 1; background: #f0fdf4; border-radius: 10pt; padding: 16pt; border-left: 4pt solid #059669;\"> <h4 style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-weight: 700; color: #1a2e2a; margin-bottom: 8pt;\">학생에게 질문 프레임워크 안내</h4> <p style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #4a5f5a; line-height: 1.7;\"> 5C 체크리스트, PREP 기법, 질문 템플릿 등을 소개하고 예시와 함께 설명합니다. 질문 품질 체크리스트를 배포하세요. </p> </div> </div> <div style=\"display: flex; gap: 20pt; margin-bottom: 16pt; position: relative; z-index: 1;\"> <div style=\"min-width: 80pt; text-align: center;\"> <div style=\"width: 80pt; height: 72pt; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0891b2 0%, #06b6d4 100%); border-radius: 12pt; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; box-shadow: 0 4pt 12pt rgba(8, 145, 178, 0.3);\"> <p style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4pt;\">STEP 3</p> <p style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: 700;\">협력</p> </div> </div> <div style=\"flex: 1; background: #f0f9ff; border-radius: 10pt; padding: 16pt; border-left: 4pt solid #0891b2;\"> <h4 style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-weight: 700; color: #1a2e2a; margin-bottom: 8pt;\">짝 활동으로 질문 작성 및 개선</h4> <p style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #4a5f5a; line-height: 1.7;\"> 학생들이 짝과 함께 초안 질문을 작성하고, 5C 체크리스트로 검토합니다. \"2 Stars and a Wish\" 피드백으로 질문을 개선하세요. </p> </div> </div> <div style=\"display: flex; gap: 20pt; margin-bottom: 16pt; position: relative; z-index: 1;\"> <div style=\"min-width: 80pt; text-align: center;\"> <div style=\"width: 80pt; height: 72pt; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed 0%, #8b5cf6 100%); border-radius: 12pt; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; box-shadow: 0 4pt 12pt rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.3);\"> <p style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4pt;\">STEP 4</p> <p style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: 700;\">탐구</p> </div> </div> <div style=\"flex: 1; background: #faf5ff; border-radius: 10pt; padding: 16pt; border-left: 4pt solid #7c3aed;\"> <h4 style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-weight: 700; color: #1a2e2a; margin-bottom: 8pt;\">AI와 대화하며 탐구 수행</h4> <p style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #4a5f5a; line-height: 1.7;\"> 개선된 질문으로 AI와 대화를 시작합니다. 학생들이 후속 질문을 통해 탐구를 심화하도록 격려하고, 교사는 순회하며 지원합니다. </p> </div> </div> <div style=\"display: flex; gap: 20pt; position: relative; z-index: 1;\"> <div style=\"min-width: 80pt; text-align: center;\"> <div style=\"width: 80pt; height: 72pt; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ea580c 0%, #f97316 100%); border-radius: 12pt; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; box-shadow: 0 4pt 12pt rgba(234, 88, 12, 0.3);\"> <p style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4pt;\">STEP 5</p> <p style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: 700;\">성찰</p> </div> </div> <div style=\"flex: 1; background: #fff7ed; border-radius: 10pt; padding: 16pt; border-left: 4pt solid #ea580c;\"> <h4 style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-weight: 700; color: #1a2e2a; margin-bottom: 8pt;\">질문-답변 과정 성찰 및 공유</h4> <p style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #4a5f5a; line-height: 1.7;\"> 학습 일지 작성, 베스트 질문 선정, 전체 발표로 마무리합니다. 질문 개선 전후 비교와 배운 점을 공유하며 메타인지를 강화하세요. </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div style=\"background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #ea580c 100%); border-radius: 10pt; padding: 16pt; margin-top: 20pt; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12pt;\"> <p style=\"font-size: 28pt;\">⏱️</p> <div> <p style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-weight: 700; color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 4pt;\">시간 배분 가이드 (45분 기준)</p> <p style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: #e0f2fe; line-height: 1.6;\"> 준비·안내(10분) → 협력 질문 작성(10분) → AI 탐구(15분) → 성찰·공유(10분) </p> </div> </div> <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding-top: 16pt; border-top: 1.5pt solid #e8f5f1;\"> <p style=\"font-size: 9pt; color: #999;\">AI 질문 엔지니어링 교육 | 교사 연수</p> <p style=\"font-size: 9pt; color: #999;\">©2025 Education Innovation</p> </div>",
